                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18010916-37-off187 t18010916-37-cd188"></join>, a silk handkerchief, value 6d. and six shillings in money
            </rs>, the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18010916-37-victim255" type="victimName">
                     Stephen 
                     Doyle
                  <interp inst="t18010916-37-victim255" type="surname" value="Doyle"></interp>
